[Student "S"]
{NORTH cannot bid 2\H at his second turn; that would be 
Fourth Suit Forcing and wouldn't show the \H suit at all.

With a game-forcing two-suiter he jumps to 3\H instead. 
SOUTH recognizes that NORTH must hold five \Ss and bids the \S game.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:Q85.A5.KQJ62.643 A943.94.87.KQJ85 K76.KJ873.A94.92 JT2.QT62.T53.AT7"]
